Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是整天待在屋子里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}not stuck in this house all day. You never leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要出去？ 我有你帮我买日常用品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Why should I leave? I have you to get me groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-你一定要搬家 -我不搬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- You have to move. - No, not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-一定要 -不搬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Yes, you do. - Not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么？ -我不搬 我喜欢这房子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Why? - Not moving. I love my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你花了不少时间 才找到你喜欢的工作室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I know it took you a long time to find a studio you loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,自从瑞安走后 你的工作效率变高了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}and ever since Ryan left, you've gotten a lot more work done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 现在好了 不再有室友了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}But, so fine, so no more roommates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞恩不是我室友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Ryan was not a roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可结果他是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Uh, it turns out he kind of was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你不能在这里抚养孩子 你连放她的地方都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Anyway, can't raise a kid here. Where would you even put her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道是个女孩？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}How do you know it's a she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是但愿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Wishful thinking, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 工作上有事 我很快就到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Sorry, it's work. I'll be there in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊，他们只能把手术延后一个小时了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Yeah, they just had to push the surgery back an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上打给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I'll call right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是不想知道孩子的性别吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You still don't wanna know the gender?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不想 那只会坏了惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}And ruin the surprise, Dr. Lapham? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近感觉怎么样？ 有没有睡得好一点呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}How have you been feeling? Have you been sleeping any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我在有这个症状之前就睡得不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I never slept well before I had this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫做怀孕 你不用不好意思说出口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It's called pregnancy. It's okay to say it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,医生你不知道吗？ 一件事情只要你不承认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Oh, don't you know, Doctor, if you don't acknowledge a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它便会消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}it simply goes away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 真的吗？我怎么不知道？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Oh, really? All this time, I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-当一匹马怀孕的时候… -天呐 又是马\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- When a horse gets pregnant... - God, the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂马吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You know about horses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,当一匹马怀孕的时候 它会马上知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}When a horse gets pregnant, it knows right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它吃东西的方式和走路的样子会改变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It changes the way it eats. It changes its gait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,其他马靠得太近 它会咬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It bites all the other horses who come too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-真可惜我们不是马 -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It's too bad we're not horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,做马真好 这样我们就会有一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It is too bad. Great to be a horse. Then we would have, like, a mother
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真正抚养我们的母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}who would have actually raised us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,和一个在遥远的马场的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}and a father off on some faraway stud farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我们的父亲确实是在一个遥远的马场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Hold on. Our father was off on a faraway stud farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-没错 -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- That is correct. - That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真可怜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Poor us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该借午餐时间喝瓶葡萄酒聊聊 我们有多可怜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We should go feel sorry for ourselves with lunch and a bottle of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你终于开始说人话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Oh, finally, now you're making some sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-好 -你们非要在我面前说喝酒吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Good. - Really, in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是那个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We didn't mean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一小杯红酒伤不了这小豌豆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}No, like a tiny glass of rosé is not gonna hurt the little bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才听到的是喝一瓶酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I'm pretty sure I heard the word "bottle."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,除了小豌豆以外 你也许还得想个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You might want to think of a name besides "little bean"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你的孩子已经有一个小甜瓜那么大了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}seeing as your child is now the size of a small melon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小甜瓜！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Small melon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你很难爱上一个你没见过的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I know it's hard to love someone you haven't met yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你真会说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Oh, that's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你有想过把那句话 缝在一个小背包上吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Thought about stitching that on, like, a little lavender sachet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-放在礼品店里可以卖出去 -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Could sell them in the gift shop. - In the gift shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,马洛里 你要生孩子了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You're having a baby, Malorie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不久 你、我还有杰西卡 以及一群强悍的产科护士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Pretty soon you and I, Jessica, and some hard-ass labor and delivery nurse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,会在三楼开同样的玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}will be on the third floor making the same wise cracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只是这一次 你不会是一个人回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Only this time, you won't be going home by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果这不是你想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}But if that's not what you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多夫妻渴望着收养一个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}there are plenty of couples who are desperate to adopt a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这无关对错 你可以做你想做的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}There are no judgments here. You can make whatever choice you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能无视它 希望它就这样消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}But what you can't do is ignore it and hope it just goes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（考虑领养？怀孕让人迷惑）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你在里面没事吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You okay in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I'm great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你吐了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Are you puking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你先到车里去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Just go to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是大块的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Is it chunky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 就是那种直接喷出来 很干净的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}No, it was actually the really smooth kind that just shoots out real clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们车里见 好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I'll meet you at the car, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-在走廊里 -走道让出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- In the corridor. - Let's get it clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！警卫！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Hey! Hey! Hey, security!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 快来帮帮忙！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Watch out. Help. I need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不 退后！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}No, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-冷静一点 请你冷静 -一级灰色预警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Calm down. Please calm down. - Code gray. Level one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静下来 警卫！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Calm down. Security!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-你感觉好点了吗？ -已经开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- You feel better? - It's happening now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有没溅到身上？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You get any on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在俄罗斯让大家发疯的东西 到我们这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}The thing in Russia that's making everybody crazy, it's here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么？ -拜托你…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- What? - Can you just, please--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等等！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Hold on. - Inside the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-医院里 -天呐 快走！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,走！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Go, go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们直接去圣罗莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We're going straight to Santa Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在这鬼东西结束之前 你待我家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You can stay at my place until whatever the fuck this is isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-我没有衣服 -你可以穿我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- I don't have any clothes. - You can wear something of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你的马场服饰不适合我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I'm not much of a chaps-and-boots gal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在还在想穿什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You're worried about what to wear right now?
