Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.20,1:02:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是世界末日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- It's not the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.79,1:02:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.54,1:02:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It sure feels like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.54,1:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在我被派去伊拉克的最后一段时间 我们驻扎在一个村里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}At the end of my deployment in Iraq, we were stationed at this village...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.54,1:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们奉命在街上巡逻 确保大家安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}ordered to patrol the streets, make sure everybody was safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.83,1:03:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天早晨 我们看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}One morning, we saw...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.41,1:03:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一个父亲带着他的四个孩子在走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}this father walking with his four kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.08,1:03:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我停下来确保一切都没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}So I pulled over to make sure everything was okay
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.91,1:03:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,确保他安全到达他想去的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}and to make sure he got wherever he was going safely.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.16,1:03:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,后来知道 他是送他孩子上学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Come to find out, he was walking his kids to school.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.58,1:03:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在那片狼藉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}In the middle of all that shit,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.70,1:03:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,混乱之中 他在送他孩子上学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}all that chaos, he was walking his kids to school.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.33,1:03:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.79,1:03:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就跟着他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}So we just followed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.75,1:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,日复一日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Day after day.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.45,1:03:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都会护送他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We escorted him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.95,1:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这成为了我们的一个习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}That just became our routine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.00,1:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 在我们最后的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}And then, at the end of our time,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.58,1:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,当我要回家了的时候 他给了我这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}he gave me this when it was time to come back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.75,1:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.83,1:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他依然还在送他孩子上学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I like to think he's still walking his kids to school.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.33,1:05:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,（在河上已二十八小时）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.29,1:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 有人听到吗？喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Hello, can anybody hear me? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.54,1:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是马洛里 有人吗？能听见吗？喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}This is Malorie. Anybody, can you hear me? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.25,1:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有人听见吗？喂 有人听见吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Can anybody hear me? Hello? Hello? Can anybody hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.95,1:05:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 信号测试 喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Hello? Testing, hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.20,1:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 有人在吗？喂？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Hello, is anyone out there? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.04,1:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,能听到吗，拜托？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Can you hear me, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.20,1:05:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-喂 信号测试 -你是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Hello? Testing. - Are you a...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.29,1:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你戴着眼罩吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Do you have a blindfold on?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.37,1:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你身后的毯子还挂着吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You do. Is-- Is the blanket behind you still up?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.70,1:05:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.87,1:05:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好 快点进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Okay, just come in really, really quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.33,1:05:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我的眼罩在这里 非常感谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Thank you. Here's my blindfold. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.87,1:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 在这里等一下 马洛里！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It's okay. Just wait. Wait here. Malorie!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.45,1:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-等等 -奥林匹亚 你在干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- I gotta pee. - Olympia, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.29,1:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-马洛里！ -你在干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Malorie! - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.62,1:05:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-你怎么想的？趴下！ -他很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- What are you thinking? Get down! - Okay, he's just scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.50,1:05:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-他很害怕 -检查他的包\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- He's just scared. - Tom. Check the bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.54,1:06:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 奥林匹亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Get over here, Olympia. Get over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.12,1:06:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是谁？ -这家伙是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Who are you? - Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.83,1:06:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆 我看着他 检查他的包\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Tom, I've got him. Check the bag. Check the bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.58,1:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是谁？ -他很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Who is this? - He's just scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.12,1:06:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是谁？ -他怎么进来的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Who are you? - How did he get in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.66,1:06:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-奥林匹亚 闭嘴 你是谁？ -他刚才很害怕 我就让他进来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Shut up, Olympia. Who are you? - He was scared, okay? I just let him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.29,1:06:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-你让一个陌生人到房子里来？ -对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- You let a stranger in the house! - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.75,1:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-他吓坏了！ -你是傻子吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- He was terrified! - Are you a simpleton?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.75,1:06:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Oh, God. Okay. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.04,1:06:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我名叫加里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}My name is Gary.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.29,1:06:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我住在城里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I live in the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.83,1:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西来的时候 我和我同事坐了出城的第一班列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}When these things came, I got the first train out with some colleagues
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.75,1:06:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们以为这样就会安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}because we thought it would be safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.83,1:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,让我待在这里吧 拜托了 他们在找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Please, please just let me stay here. They're after me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.41,1:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在找你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Who's after you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.50,1:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不信 他在说谎 -谁在找你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- I don't believe it. He's lying. - Who's after you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.66,1:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,显然他在说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It's obvious he's lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.87,1:06:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-我发誓 -你为什么来这里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- I swear. - Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.45,1:06:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们藏到我同事卡尔家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We went to my colleague Carl's house to lay low.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.50,1:06:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,原先一切都没事 后来他们闯了进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Everything was fine until they broke in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.54,1:06:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,灵体不会闯进人家的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Creatures don't break into people's homes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.41,1:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是灵体 是这些疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}No, not the creatures, these psychos.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.37,1:06:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,诺斯伍德的疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}These psychos from Northwood.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.41,1:07:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,诺斯伍德？是哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Northwood? I don't... Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.91,1:07:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个精神病院 专门收容那些犯罪的精神病人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It's a mental institution for the criminally insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.00,1:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这下可好 他们有了放风通行证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Well, it's nice to know they have hall passes now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.70,1:07:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}And then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.66,1:07:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我们带到外面 逼我们睁开眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}They took us outside and they forced our eyes open
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.08,1:07:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我们不得不看那些灵体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}so that we would have to look at the creatures.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.00,1:07:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.08,1:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-你看了吗？ -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Did you look? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.12,1:07:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我朋友卡尔把他们其中的一个人 摔倒在地上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Somehow, my friend Carl managed to tackle one of these people to the ground
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.00,1:07:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们都跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}and the rest of us made a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.50,1:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不停地跑 直到跑到了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I just kept on running and running and running till I got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.79,1:07:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我敲了每家每户的门 但没人开门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I've been knocking on all the doors and nobody answered.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.95,1:07:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,最后你们开了门 所以…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Until you did, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.79,1:07:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.37,1:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.66,1:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,最可怕的是 当这些人闯进来的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}The scariest thing was, uh... when these people broke in, they...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.00,1:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有戴着眼罩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}they weren't wearing blindfolds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.83,1:08:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好像他们不需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It's like they didn't need them.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.16,1:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果它们在外面 你一定要戴眼罩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}But they'd been outside. You have to wear blindfolds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.66,1:08:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人不用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Not these people.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.91,1:08:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这些疯子不会像其他人一样受到影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}These crazy guys weren't affected like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.16,1:08:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}They wanted to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.16,1:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}They were happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.25,1:08:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可开心了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}They were so glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.20,1:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说所有人都必需看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}And they said everyone needed to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.29,1:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.54,1:08:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,起来 出去 这里不是孤儿院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Get up and get out. It's not an orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.41,1:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,新来的 你来参观过了 我们很高兴认识你 现在滚吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}New guy, you had a great visit. We really loved meeting you. Now fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.37,1:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谁不同意 就和他一起走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}And anybody who doesn't agree, you go with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.41,1:08:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-快点出去！ -道格拉斯 你这是谋杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Out now! - Douglas, that is murder.
