Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.95,1:28:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在的话 请回话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}If there is anyone there, please respond.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.00,1:28:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-喂 -喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Hello? - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.70,1:28:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.37,1:28:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-我名叫瑞克 -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}My name is Rick.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.70,1:28:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.16,1:28:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞克 我是汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Rick, this is Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.45,1:28:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We have a place.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.87,1:28:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一个营地 有足够的供给…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}A compound with enough supplies--
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.91,1:28:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一个社区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We have a community.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.04,1:28:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It's safe here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.41,1:28:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在河的最下游\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We're down by the river's end.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.75,1:28:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在哪儿？ -别回答他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Where are you? - Don't answer that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.12,1:29:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,派克采石场附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Near Pike's Quarry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.91,1:29:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 你们好远 你们有几个人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Jesus. You're a ways away. How many of you are there?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.58,1:29:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,四个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Four of us. - Hmm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.41,1:29:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,其中有小孩吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Are any of them children?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.04,1:29:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么都别说 -没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Don't, do not say anything. - It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.75,1:29:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.00,1:29:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为沿着河过来是到这里最快的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Because the fastest way to get here is by the river,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.70,1:29:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕你带着小孩来不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}and I don't think you could make it with kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.12,1:29:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 沿着河？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Wait, the river?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.20,1:29:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,向下游一直漂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Float downstream as far as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.12,1:29:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你们到达急流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Stay on the water until you hit the rapids.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.20,1:29:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那里水流湍急 非常危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}The water is fast there. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.12,1:29:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有几个人丢了性命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We've lost some people.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.29,1:29:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们得看清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You need to see clearly.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.45,1:29:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么意思？ -你说看清楚是什么意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- What does that mean? - What do you mean, see clearly?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.25,1:29:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们得看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You will have to look.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.29,1:29:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞克 我们都戴着眼罩 我们看不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- I'm telling you. - Rick, we'll have blindfolds on.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.16,1:29:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样说我就放心了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We can't look.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.16,1:29:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you said that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.12,1:29:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一定要有一个人…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Someone will have to take a--
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.41,1:29:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,按流速计算 你们要准备好大概两天的旅程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Prepare for two days' journey at the pace of the river's current.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.58,1:29:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,带超过两天需要的补给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Bring supplies for longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.62,1:30:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,急流过后怎么找你呢？瑞克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}How do I find you after the rapids, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.95,1:30:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会听见鸟声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You'll hear the birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.87,1:30:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有很多鸟 跟着声音走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We've got a lot of them. Just follow the sound to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.12,1:30:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,顺着河边小道 你们会碰到一面墙 墙上有一扇门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Down a small embankment, you'll find a wall with a gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.58,1:30:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}That's our--
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.87,1:30:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们的什么？ -我们的什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- That's their what? - That's our what?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.29,1:30:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Rick?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.50,1:30:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Rick?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.83,1:30:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It could be real.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.83,1:30:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-不 -或许是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- No. - Could be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.91,1:30:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-“或许”还不够 -万一瑞克能帮我呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Could be is not good enough. - What if Rick could help us?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.20,1:30:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,万一瑞克和那帮人是一伙的呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}And what if Rick is one of them?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.70,1:30:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但他知道鸟的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Huh? Wait, he knew about the birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.95,1:30:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 加里也知道鸟的事 他把鸟放进冰柜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Oh, my God. Gary knew about the birds and he put them in the freezer.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.79,1:30:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信你真的在考虑这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}I cannot believe you're actually thinking about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.08,1:30:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,每家房子都没食物了 我们得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Every house has run out of food. We have to move.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.04,1:30:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的以为我不知道吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You really don't think I know that? You don't think I know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.75,1:30:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候 我们家有条像这样的船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}When I was little, we had a boat just like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.50,1:31:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,每年夏天 我们会把船拉到湖上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}And every single summer, we would take it to the lake.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.04,1:31:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,每年夏天都会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Every summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.41,1:31:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一定会很喜欢那里的 那里有树 有花\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You guys would have loved it up there. They had trees. They had flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.54,1:31:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,湖水很暖和 天上飘着云\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}The water was warm, the clouds were in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.29,1:31:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所有孩子都在水里玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We'd all play in the water. All the kids, all the children.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.20,1:31:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都会在水里与岸上来回跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We would all just run up and down the shore.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.29,1:31:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上有别的孩子吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}There were other children in the world?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.00,1:31:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊 就像你们一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Yeah, just like you. Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.58,1:31:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,像你们一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.83,1:31:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天我们看到了一棵巨大的橡树\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}One day, we saw this really, really big oak tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.00,1:31:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,比这个房子还要大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It was bigger than this house.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.62,1:31:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大到我们连树顶都看不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It was so big and old, I couldn't see the top of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.16,1:31:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-猜我们做了什么？ -爬了树\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Guess what we did? - Climbed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.66,1:31:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我们爬了上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We climbed it. Yes, we climbed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.37,1:31:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不断地爬 一直爬到树顶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}We climbed it and climbed it until we got to the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.70,1:31:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,猜我们爬到树顶后看到了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Guess what we saw when we got to the top?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.37,1:31:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,男孩！女孩！该睡觉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Boy! Girl! Time for bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.95,1:31:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但汤姆在讲故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}But Tom's telling a story.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.58,1:31:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-就让我…快讲完了 -我不说第二遍 走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Mal, let me just-- We're almost done. - I'm not gonna say it again. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.54,1:31:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩 走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Girl, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.95,1:31:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.16,1:31:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.95,1:31:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.37,1:31:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,上床！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Bed!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.91,1:32:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在干什么？ -你在干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- What are you doing? - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.87,1:32:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们就会以为 他们会和别的孩子去爬树\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Now they think they're gonna go outside and climb trees with all these new kids
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.04,1:32:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-看花草 看蝴蝶！ -这只是个故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- and see butterflies and flowers! - It's a story.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.12,1:32:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是故事 这是个谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}It's not a story. It's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.16,1:32:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们永远不会爬树 他们永远不会交新朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Because they'll never climb trees, they are never gonna make new friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.08,1:32:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么要他们相信这些？ -他们总得相信些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- Why make them believe that? - They have to believe in something.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.87,1:32:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他们什么都不信 做这些有什么意义？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}What is this for if they don't have anything to believe in?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.00,1:32:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-为了他们能生存 -生存并不是生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}- So that they survive! - Surviving is not living.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.50,1:32:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,听你的 他们会死的！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}They're gonna die if they listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.25,1:32:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,生活不仅是生活本身 更是它蕴含的可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Life is more than just what is. It's what could be.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.41,1:32:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把它变成什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}What you could make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.41,1:32:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你知道不可能实现 你也要给他们梦想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You need to promise them dreams that may never come true.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.45,1:32:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你明知道随时可能失去他们 但你会一样地去爱他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You need to love them knowing that you may lose them at any second.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.87,1:32:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们值得拥有梦想、爱和希望 他们值得拥有一个母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}They deserve dreams. They deserve love. They deserve hope. They deserve a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.50,1:32:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们值得拥有一个母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}They deserve a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.87,1:32:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没给他们取名 马洛里 他们还是叫男孩、女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}You haven't given them names, Mal. Their names are Boy and Girl!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.83,1:32:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想想吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Think about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.83,1:32:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的每一个决定都是为了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs9}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad0}Every single decision I have made has been for them.
